headline: Kalahari Resorts & Conventions Welcomes Todd Conrad as National Sales Director
summary: WISCONSIN DELLS, Wis., September 03, 2025--Kalahari Resorts & Conventions, home to America’s Largest Indoor Waterparks, is excited to welcome Todd Conrad as National Sales Director. Based in the suburbs of Chicago, Conrad will work remotely to support Kalahari across all markets.
